<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-37-0484 </DOCNO><TEXT>A description is given of a method to determine continuously and on-linethe fuel consumption of a coal-fired power plant on the basis of thenormal measuring instruments in the plant. The method has been developedand tested off-line in a large coal-fired unit with a relatively complexsteam system. At present equipment is installed for a continuous, automateddetermination and registration, for the processing of the energy flow,supplied by the fuel, and for determining the efficiency of the unit.1 fig., 2 refs., 2 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>